slides.content: “Dr. Parker has helped me in navigating issues of belonging and identity. Thanks to her I’m now able to make good and healthy choices for myself and the relationships I am in. I’m grateful that I found her when I did and I highly recommend her”

slides.content: “I have been working with Dr. Parker during the past few years. She was extremely helpful in helping me find solutions to various problems I have faced. She has definitely made an impact in my life that I will always cherish. ”
